{"tid":2355976,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩立新法檢查手機　禁年輕人短訊用南韓俚語　違者面臨勞改","createTime":"2021-01-06T13:00:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T10:22:46.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10028736f9abe0547c0a9e8b2626a24881c11e79","tid":2355976,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/1/1609933404_aI-1280w.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F1%2F1609933404_aI-1280w.JPG&h=170be051&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://d2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net/2021/1/1609933400_Wl-1280w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fd2e7nuz2r6mjca.cloudfront.net%2F2021%2F1%2F1609933400_Wl-1280w.png&h=d85b291a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓繼禁止國民觀看「韓劇」後，其領導人金正恩現在更禁止年輕人在手機短訊中使用南韓俚語，認為那是墮落的語言。有報道指，這條新法上月起實施，因平壤政府擔心愈來愈多年輕國民使用南韓的俚語，新法下當局可以檢查民眾的手機，查看他們的私人通訊是否有使用「禁語」，違者面臨勞改。<br />\n<br />\n報道北韓消息的日本地下雜誌《臨津江》(Rimjingang)引述北韓的父母稱，一些無害的俚語可能令他們的子女陷入麻煩，指新法的目標是針對手機短訊。雖然被禁，但北韓人都有偷偷看韓劇，南韓劇集已傳入北韓一段時間，受訪的父母稱，「由於手機近年變普及，年輕人都在短訊中使用南韓用語。例如幾乎全部年輕人都在短訊中，使用saranghae(我愛你)、chal-ka(再見)、以及bye-bye和ty(英語多謝(thank you)簡寫)等用語。」如果手機機主的短訊被發現有這些非北韓用語，將會被質疑偷看韓劇和遭盤問。受訪的父母又說，檢查人員也會查看短訊是否有關於新冠肺炎疫情的不好傳言。不過，學生和年輕人都有應對方法，在發出短訊後盡快刪除它們。<br />\n<br />\n《臨津江》聲稱取得一份3頁的機密文件，金正恩指南韓是美國傀儡，並列出更多禁語，「我們必須在社區裡大力掃除傀儡(南韓)的用語和傀儡生活方式。」金正恩又提到他過去多次警告，無血緣的年輕男女不可以使用「傀儡用語」稱呼對方，如oppa(哥哥)和dong-saeng(弟弟、妹妹)，指這些典型傀儡用語在北韓國內廣傳。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB-%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%95%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F-%E7%A6%81%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E7%9F%AD%E8%A8%8A%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E4%BF%9A%E8%AA%9E-%E9%81%95%E8%80%85%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E5%8B%9E%E6%94%B9-250600\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB-%25E9%2587%2591%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E6%2581%25A9%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%259F%25A5%25E6%2589%258B%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%259F%25AD%25E8%25A8%258A%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E4%25BF%259A%25E8%25AA%259E-%25E9%2581%2595%25E8%2580%2585%25E9%259D%25A2%25E8%2587%25A8%25E5%258B%259E%25E6%2594%25B9-250600&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImXHr90zhVRml9IH8Z62du0k%3D&h=a8bd588c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.am730.com.hk/news/%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%8C%97%E9%9F%93%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB-%E9%87%91%E6%AD%A3%E6%81%A9%E7%AB%8B%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%95%E6%AA%A2%E6%9F%A5%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F-%E7%A6%81%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E7%9F%AD%E8%A8%8A%E7%94%A8%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E4%BF%9A%E8%AA%9E-%E9%81%95%E8%80%85%E9%9D%A2%E8%87%A8%E5%8B%9E%E6%94%B9-250600</a>"},{"pid":"ef412e85eebd646d2524784edd20bfefc2d6e81d","tid":2355976,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:03:40.000Z","msg":"痾篤茄~~~~~~~~"},{"pid":"dc228935e2560ec50b935aa0e3b1291421d64d46","tid":2355976,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T13:04:25.000Z","msg":"Shake it<br />\nIc"},{"pid":"d2fd99107867279952a5abd7c13e74a23ec206cf","tid":2355976,"uid":5220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T23:48:13.000Z","msg":"ㅅㅂ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abd345cc63ada64069c8587ff60315ef7c3dc83a","tid":2355976,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"施巴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}